{
  "stem": "22889.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We traveled in a caboose, like a regular-- like a freight train for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- we weren't allowed to-- we weren't allowed to travel with-- with the other people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Jewish people had to be separate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walk from the station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From our station to my home was, like, maybe three miles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walk home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I come home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole family was already home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And besides that, you know, in our neighborhood, the Jewish people used to live in the villages, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A couple of days before that, they brought all the Jewish people from the small villages to our-- to our town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our town was a county seat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but all the people-- all the Jewish people from the villages-- I had an uncle in Zakopane-- two uncles I had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So him and his wife and two children, then the other uncle, he was a doctor, him and his wife-- they came in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all lived in our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had 19 people living in our house-- in our little five-room house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I want you to know how we used to slept.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some sleep in the bed, some slept in the-- on the floor-- on the straw sack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to make a-- like a mattress-- a sack filled up with straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We called it straw sack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since we're asleep, we slept toe to-- feet to feet-- like that-- 19 people in one house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then beside that, we had three dogs also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't imagine it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was one harmony.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was pretty nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- everybody come to our house.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
